Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我預料的還要冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  大家都還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸虧有蘿潔小姐準備的禦寒衣物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  公主殿下的也很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊安真是到哪都不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是鶺鴒之羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連禦寒衣物的品質都是一流的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既輕又暖是挺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過跟手套的接合還有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要改良的地方等會再整理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這趟也算獲取了不少採樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事問你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背叛災禍的現主了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便你們去到主人那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也改變不了任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來還不知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙  那我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要跟我們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起前往北極
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全無法理解你的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有資格說這種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你憑依那個叫蘿潔的姑娘又想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連那姑娘的個人意願都要被你剝奪了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  越過那座山就是地獄的入口了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:16.26,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}哀しみに囚われた魂たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:26.31,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}終わらない憎しみが叫びだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:35.57,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}迷いの森を抜け　世界、照らしにゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:45.37,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}絶望を抱きしめるのは　諦めていない証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:54.09,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}孤独越えたら　信じあえるよ　絆離さないで…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:03:04.64,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}希望という眩しい重さに　負けない情熱この手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:15.32,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}想い、光へ…　何度でも　命尽き果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:24.65,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\blur2\pos(248,569)}北方地區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  隨時可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴  我要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要從身體上迎合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼說我也不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說這是想像訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣把意識放到全方位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神依化後的我會化身武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌控這武器的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說我要控制這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意右邊  左邊也別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神依化似乎有點勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是現在這德性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若史雷陷入險境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也無法幫助他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就沒需要從士的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷先生  請用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能做的也就這點小事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能沒有神依的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也毫無進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那會事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完神依化的訓練還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就足夠厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用在意這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾一直都憑依在蘿潔身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆不是以理論而是身體本來就記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和艾德娜小姐學不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是  不過現在來說確實沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢  我感覺神依本身很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像背著隻野豬走在一條空中細線上一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這感覺  我也多少有一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天得吃好幾頓才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  各位請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於馬上就要開始最終之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和大伙給你們做了能打起精神的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南瓜慕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用這低溫環境製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慕斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  米克里歐你也試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這味道  前所未有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷  再給我一口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米克里歐自己去拿不就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我無法自己去找她要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故意整我的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天族也挺麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到能在這種地方吃上慕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下懂做料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  這沒有包含在我的訓練項目裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等回到瑞迪雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就一起學做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要比比看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我閱讀這另一本天遺見聞錄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現有一些關於北方的記述
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這上面寫道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一種構築世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而源泉就在北方地區
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界上還有許多我們不知道的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  記述上還說源泉通過地脈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把世界連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地脈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這  或許就是災禍的現主到北方的理由之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地脈的事我聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說它維護這世界的均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為這均衡被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才孕育出災難的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是這源泉和地脈把汙穢吸過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這很難說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經來過幾次這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然從氣候上來說是個嚴峻的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但依然有人在這裡安居
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是片能讓人感受到溫暖的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他只想散播汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不該來這種北極之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去洛倫斯的首都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者瑞迪雷克不是更有效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,災禍的現主為什麼要到北方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  明天要跨越山巔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不回應我的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您把心鎖起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是已經徹底化身汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前要我告訴你 為什麼我要跟著你們對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就告訴你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人在之前那一戰放過了導師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為他從導師身上看到了可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠殺掉他可能性的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是淨化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的主人沒有那麼天真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為什麼災禍的現主 到這種北極之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙  在你心裡災禍的現主是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著你管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說到這份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是天真嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願你也能做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不用面對這種磨難了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從山那邊溢出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米克里歐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了  阿塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾爾敏之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了  米克里歐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  趁現在翻越山巔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希萊爾  伊安  整理好隊列
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  完全看不到前路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧太濃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  請聚集到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是散開就會被汙穢纏身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各隊  密集陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人  天族  導師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對汙穢來說都有特效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信  竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍是天族憑魔化的姿態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看這數量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是所有天族都染上汙穢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這玩笑真開大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是輸了這場戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信這世上還存在這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠  都跟到這種鬼地方來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底想幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能淨化得完這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊菈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗艾斯=梅瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是災禍的現主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汙穢如此密集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,災禍的現主肯定在這前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了  史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米克里歐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯茲西布=萊雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼穹十二連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗艾斯=梅瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾  我也想戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要神依嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是死了就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了還怎麼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在死前先說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯維尤=尤克姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不行  蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜小姐  請讓我也神依
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個亂來的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別殺死我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我不討厭你這種性子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將和史雷一起打通突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部隊就交給你們指揮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈克蒂姆=尤芭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是神依
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:14:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺充滿了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣解決它們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那些傢伙要那麼拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淨化世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會裝好心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子也想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子也想做做好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幫傢伙的前路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由老子幫他們開通好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子來把這些東西撕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎  看大部隊那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然背叛我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一開始就不是跟你們一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真狼狽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的主人  請回應我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您真的聽不到我的聲音了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法忍受主人這麼強大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然會被汙穢所控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙  你為何要悲嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把導師帶來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是人類的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人要打倒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你期望著絕望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說連我都被您利用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是主人需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我願粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切隨主人願
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子也想助人為樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽的  撕多少都撕不完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼老子要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽的  媽的  媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去力量不夠用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫上  一點  忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別死了  蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是差點就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神依真是太要命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續  我還能繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若世界的汙穢都聚集到北方這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只要我們在這裡清除它們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界就能煥然一新對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是最好的機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的正義比搆不到的理想更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我現在眼前的正義就是理想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會繼續的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾先生  蘿潔怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,災禍的現主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  是西蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:28.64,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}もうどうしようもないって事もある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.97,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}なるようにしかならなかったり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.38,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}また押し寄せてくる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:41.29,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}ただどうやって受け止めたらいい?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:44.75,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}It's mean to be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:52.61,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}僕だけのものじゃなくなった夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:59.07,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}明日を導いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:03.12,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}現実とFight　運命にDive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:06.19,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5\fs20\pos(732,2)}おもい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:06.19,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}ほとばしる情熱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:13.00,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}何度息絶えそうでも　ただ真っ直ぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:17.06,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Don't give up the fight　Time to ignite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:20.41,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}この身をかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:24.06,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}挑む世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:30.86,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}いっそあるがままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:35.77,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}その全てを包み込むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  米克里歐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想比起剛走出伊子集那會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷真是成長了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米克里歐一直都在照顧史雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾不是也一直在照顧蘿潔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.58,0:23:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然史雷成長了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是那麼莽撞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不敢讓他離開眼界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  好讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾  來練習神依吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用再歇一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  這點苦算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  趕緊做完預告開始練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週  化為風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待

